<subSubSection id="A670C50AEDD6793E9356393E928CEDA6" pageId="0" pageNumber="35" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="4A46CEEEA4BA294F7F8A559A0A00A201" pageId="0" pageNumber="35">Remark.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FBC703DA69CEF2D365D567EEF3BF82FC" pageId="0" pageNumber="35">
This species is known as a predator of scale insects, including 
<taxonomicName id="2D4EB1DF2E77328E975B806060005EBF" class="Insecta" family="Margarodidae" genus="Icerya" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Icerya purchasi" order="Hemiptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="35" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="purchasi">
<emphasis id="641E7FE524DB9FF1973A48D64728E60C" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="35">Icerya purchasi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Maskell, as mentioned in the label data by 
<normalizedToken id="2389A3923EF061E8E967995F34D998FC" originalValue="FÃ¼rsch">Fuersch</normalizedToken>
(1968); it is a pest of 
<taxonomicName id="CC154D8716079D67A596DAF2D65E5671" class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Rutaceae" genus="Citrus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Citrus" order="Rutales" pageId="0" pageNumber="35" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="A27CC4E6A194D254E9FE009581B3E609" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="35">Citrus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
spp. and 
<taxonomicName id="2ED5D1FD739480B01208E15560375BF4" class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Casuarinaceae" genus="Casuarina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Casuarina" order="Casuarinales" pageId="0" pageNumber="35" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="FAB2538ECC218FF75DCC8DF40C470981" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="35">Casuarina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. (
<bibRefCitation id="26AFD344B9843A011F0B495235FD6AAE" author="Martin, HE" journalOrPublisher="Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution" pageId="0" pageNumber="35" refId="B29" refString="Martin, HE, 1972. Report to the government of Saudi Arabia on research in plant protection FAO. Entomologist FAO/SAO/IF/63 (AGP.TA) 207, 38." title="Report to the government of Saudi Arabia on research in plant protection FAO. Entomologist FAO / SAO / IF / 63 (AGP. TA) 207, 38." year="1972">Martin 1972</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
